      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s M-Division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, ensuring optimal cam phasing and throttle response across the entire power band. Power is transmitted through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is in flawless condition, including proactive subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring Bilstein dampers and poly-bushing upgrades for sharpened turn-in. The exterior retains its factory luster with perfect panel gaps, while the interior shows zero bolster wear or pixel degradation in the instrumentation. This is a mechanically transparent, investment-grade vehicle for the discerning driver.",
